body:
TensorFlow Serving already links against `tensorflow/contrib:contrib_kernels`:

https://github.com/tensorflow/serving/blob/r1.10/tensorflow_serving/model_servers/BUILD#L260L263

However, the `beam_search_ops` kernels were added to this rule in TensorFlow 1.3.
